Title: Enhancing the Obsolescing Bargain Theory: A Longitudinal Study of Foreign Ownership of U.S. and European Multinationals
Pages: 159-180
Author-Name: Sushil Vachani
Author-Workplace-Name: Boston University
File-URL: http://www.palgrave-journals.com/jibs/journal/v26/n1/pdf/8490170a.pdf
File-Format: Application/pdf
